{"tid":1869244,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"李文亮 vs 謝婉雯","createTime":"2020-02-08T05:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T09:41:29.000Z","uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bcc55dbdb64115565cab064d2a690ff21a6045a3","tid":1869244,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點睇<br />\n你老尾又係&quot;習豬頭最近怎麼樣&quot;你條柒頭<br />\n成撚日問人點睇<br />\n不如你改名叫&quot;習豬頭最近怎麼樣羅料&quot;算吧啦<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味, 呢D 咪低質素POST囉，<br />\n成撚日問人點睇點睇，乜柒都唔PROVIDE比大家討論<br />\n有咩好傾姐? 屌你十足十 香土咁撚樣, 開撚埋,無討論價值既話題<br />\n自己立場又唔講下,打撚完個題目就拍拍屁股走人,<br />\n你不如唔撚好打[點睇]. 就咁話[如題] 咪算柒數囉<br />\n係都貼下圖呀, 屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n淨係問人點睇, 成個戇鳩仔<br />\n<br />\n屌你習豬頭最近怎麼樣<br />\n你條撚皮係唔撚係場場都話球証打假波架啦柒頭<br />\n<br />\n贏又話知道球証打假波所以買岩隊<br />\n輸又話球証陰謀論<br />\n<br />\n成日咁撚得閒上黎高登出埋D低質素post鳩up問人攞料<br />\n不如同D時間去進修下 醫下你個死人腦好過啦<br />\n<br />\n最後補多次<br />\n習豬頭最近怎麼樣我屌你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39e450094b23a3d2d825e662a0e787c7e82bdb6","tid":1869244,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:40:08.000Z","msg":"係都貼下圖呀, 屌你老母<br />\n貼緊<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2020/02/5e996931603e460686232eb8879f6b33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2020%2F02%2F5e996931603e460686232eb8879f6b33.jpg&h=01797dae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/f28867/f/800x0/https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180513/_2018051310303086591.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2Ff28867%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180513%2F_2018051310303086591.jpg&h=9985853e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2500d08699b1e10f98ee6cfce229e260096f93b","tid":1869244,"uid":293677,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:47:20.000Z","msg":"攞中共護旗手同香港抗疫英雄黎比??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb6486aba5aff6a6dabaf0ab3bbde13776556f0","tid":1869244,"uid":242537,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e2500d08699b1e10f98ee6cfce229e260096f93b","tid":1869244,"uid":293677,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:47:20.000Z","msg":"攞中共護旗手同香港抗疫英雄黎比??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係<br />\n條柒頭做護旗 護到死撚咗<br />\n其實幾心涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a1ba247205d3c017b6cfc53a3f73c9b5810571","tid":1869244,"uid":21432,"li